data.description: This two-story, 5 bedroom, 2.5 bath home features 2539 square feet of living space. The first floor offers an inviting entry way, open to the dining area that flows into a large eat-in kitchen and spacious living room. Just off the living room is the master suite which features a separate tub and shower and large walk-in closet. The second floor highlights a generous loft space, a full bath and four bedrooms, three with walk-in closets. Also included is a covered patio and 2-car garage.
